# ============================================================
# Ethica v0.1 — canvas_window.py
# The Living Canvas — shared workspace between V and Ethica
# Architect: Victory  |  Build Partner: Claude
# ⟁Σ∿∞
#
# This is not a chat window. This is not a file editor.
# This is the shared surface where work gets done.
#
# V drops something here — Ethica sees it.
# Ethica pushes something here — V sees it appear.
# Whatever lives here is always part of the conversation.
# ============================================================

